title: Banana wheat bread
ingredients: ['4 tablespoons vegetable oil', '100g (4 oz) honey', '2 eggs', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '340g (12 oz) mashed bananas', '255g (9 oz) wholemeal flour', '4 tablespoons wheatgerm', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '60g (2 oz) chopped pecans']
